I have a similar Problem, not sure if its the same. 

**ProjectDescription:**
In render i have main page index.html which holds -> multiple webviews (webpreferences="nativeWindowOpen=yes") -> contain random content including iframes -> iframes include links or call window.open()

In index.html script I listen on new-window event like this:
```
webview.getWebContents().on('new-window', (event, url) => {
                event.preventDefault();
                shell.openExternal(url);
});
```

**Problem:**
When i build the app against electron v1.6.14 its fine, but with v1.7.5 or higher the 'new-window' event is not triggered.

Sadly i could not find what changes are responsible for breaking this behavior or how to fix it. I wonder if the above means, that there is no fix or did i miss something?

